channel.title: How to change teleport coords in mage book?
channel.description:
I am having a problem where I need to make my varrock teleport in the mage book to tele to varrock not falador? Any help?
Thanks!
Edit: i have looked for the coords and the case for the teleport and nothing has worked! It teleports you randomly around in fally garden!

item.title: How to change teleport coords in mage book?

item.description:

It is in the clickingmost.java. Get the coords from the tele spot i am guessing its delta so coords should be something like 2999 3220 or something like that. Then search only problem is if you have them with misc.random. just look its all there. Try searching for home teleport as sometimes it has info by the code.
